result.title: Hackatari Codeathon 2017
result.content:
Hello Geeks!

Thank you for participating in our Codeathon, we are extremely excited for the challenge.

Hackatari Codeathon is a Competitive Programming Contest that will be open to all programmers in Jordan including school and university students. The contest concept is all about using code to solve given problem set. Problems will be sorted by our perceived difficulty. This measurement might differ between people, so please do read all the problems.

Winners will be selected based on number of problems solved and time penalty.

Rounds Details

Qualification Round: Saturday, Feb 4 at 6:00 pm

  • Location: Codeforces.com/Group Contests
  • Duration: 150 Minutes

Onsite Round:Saturday, Feb 11 at 10:00 am

**This round is only for the top 15 participants who qualifies from the Online Round

  • Location: Mixed Dimensions office
  • Duration: 300 Minutes

Please do not hesitate to contact us on rawand@mxd3d.com for further explanation

Best of Luck !
